    "description": {
      "value": "<div><hr /><div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You have mastered ranged weapons and can make shots that others find impossible. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">Attacking at long range doesn't impose disadvantage on your ranged weapon attack rolls.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">Your ranged weapon attacks ignore &amp;Reference[rule=halfcover]{half cover} and &amp;Reference[rule=Cover]{three-quarters cover}.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">Before you make an attack with a ranged weapon that you are proficient with, you can choose to take a -5 penalty to the attack roll. If the attack hits, you add +10 to the attack's damage.</li></ul></div>\n\t\t\t</div></div>",
